简介 INFO
Welcome to Super Wipeout! This map is based off the TV show "Wipeout" in which you have to make it past obstacles to win.In this map you also have to get through all of the obstacles, which are redstone and command block controlled.This map also has additional features, like enabling effects.This map is Singleplayer and Multiplayer!I hope you enjoy my map "Super Wipeout."
欢迎来到超级抹除！这张地图是基于“Wipeout”这个电视节目，就是你要穿越各种障碍来胜利。这张地图的障碍是由CB和红石来控制。这张地图还有各种特效，比如随机效果。本地图支持多人和单人。希望你们喜欢这张地图。
